3. Time-Limited Builds and Automatic Expiration

3.1. Limited Availability. The Plugin is provided as time-limited Plugin Builds. Each
Plugin Build contains an embedded Expiration Date after which the Plugin will
automatically stop functioning.

3.2. Automatic Expiration. Upon reaching the Expiration Date:
- The Plugin will cease to function automatically;
- No prior notice is required before expiration;
- The Developer is under no obligation to provide replacement Plugin Builds;
- You may download a newer Plugin Build (if available) to continue using the Plugin.

3.3. No Perpetual License. This Plugin does not offer perpetual licenses. All
Plugin Builds are subject to automatic expiration. Continued use requires
obtaining newer Plugin Builds as they become available.

4. Update Checks and Network Communication

4.1. Automatic Update Checks. The Plugin periodically communicates with the
Update Server at https://mcp-steroid.jonnyzzz.com to:
- Check for available Plugin updates;
- Retrieve version information;
- Notify You of newer Plugin Builds.

4.2. Data Transmitted. During update checks, the following information may be
transmitted to the Update Server:
- Current Plugin version;
- JetBrains Product version and type;
- Operating system information.

4.3. Consent. By installing and using the Plugin, You consent to these automatic
update checks and the transmission of the information described above. The
update check functionality is integral to the Plugin's operation.

4.4. Privacy. The update check mechanism is not intended to collect personal data.
Standard server logs (if any) may include technical connection metadata. For
detailed privacy practices, see the Documentation.

